                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The letter is numbered I87/4007 within this file.</p>
               </note>Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28 April, 1887.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">H. Moors Esqr,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Acting Under Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">In compliance with the request of your memorandum of yesterday,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to C. Pearson, 29 March 1887, and the notes thereto. M sought Pearson's approval for a list that he enclosed of institutions and individuals to receive copies of his work on Acacias. That letter was referred to the Premier, D. Gillies, who requested information about the cost of preparing the work.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have the honor to report, that the preparing of each of the plates of Acacias,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Eventually published as B87.13.04 and B88.13.01.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>first by</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
